            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001181_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><add place="marginright" rend="gray small" hand="#U">Acc. 7775</add><space extent="4" unit="words"/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><add place="marginleft" rend="gray small" hand="#U">37</add></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><placeName>12 Kensington Palace Garden</placeName>
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="words"/><date when="1858-01-19">19<hi rend="sup">th</hi> January
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/>1858</date></p>
<lb/>    
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>My Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/>I think I had
<lb/>acknowledged the
<lb/>receipt of your
<lb/>favour containing
<lb/>the note from
<lb/><persName>Lady Chetwynd</persName> before
<lb/>your last came
<lb/>to hand but certainly
<lb/>not before it was
<lb/>due - and while

	<pb facs="liv_001181_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>thanking you for
<lb/>the courtesy you
<lb/><choice><orig>shewed</orig><reg>showed</reg></choice> in directing
<lb/>me to send my
<lb/>things to your <choice><sic>brothers</sic><corr>brother's</corr></choice>
<lb/>warehouse it has
<lb/>occurred to me
<lb/>that possibly he
<lb/>has some of the
<lb/>articles we need
<lb/>as presents and
<lb/>that if we got
<lb/>them from him
<lb/>it would save all
<lb/>the carriage

	<pb facs="liv_001181_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/><space extent="5" unit="words"/><add place="marginright" rend="gray small" hand="#U">38</add>
<lb/>Has he beads, brass wire
<lb/>&amp; ammunition such as
<lb/>are used in the <placeName><region>West 
<lb/><orgName>African</orgName></region></placeName> trade, if so
<lb/>I would like to arrange
<lb/>with him - <add place="above">or another</add> on getting 
<lb/>samples - I am
<lb/>proceeding on the
<lb/>hope of being excused
<lb/>if I am thinking
<lb/>of him too meanly
<lb/>and that if he is
<lb/>not actually engaged
<lb/>in importing beads

	<pb facs="liv_001181_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>he may give me a
<lb/>hint as to finding
<lb/>a man who will
<lb/>deal fairly with me
<lb/>instead. I could get
<lb/>them in <placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName> but
<lb/>the carriage might
<lb/>be saved by getting
<lb/>them in <placeName><settlement type="city">Liverpool</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>Hoping you will not
<lb/>imitate my bad
<lb/>example in correspondence</p>

<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="1" unit="words"/>I am yours most
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/>Truly -</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>

<lb/><trailer rend="small">J.B. Horsball Esq.</trailer><!--Added trailer...is this okay?--><!-- Yep. AW -->

            </div>
